SimpleLog.pm:
============
0.3: first public version (beta)
0.4: add support for dynamic log levels
0.5: add support for ANSI colors on Windows
     change NOTICE color to green (blue was hard to read on some terminals)
     use default stdout log silently in constructor when logging system hasn't been initialized yet
0.6: adapt default useTimestamp and useANSICode values according to STDOUT being redirected to a file or not
0.7: do not try to use ANSI codes mode in default log if the terminal doesn't support it
0.8: avoid opening multiple file handles to same log file
0.9: use UTF-8 encoding
